</style><p>在Dokibird“回归流媒体”的消息公布后，Dokibird官方YouTube频道的订阅人数以创纪录的速度猛增。截至2月6日18:40，频道订阅人数已达约24.6万人，截至2月6日18:40，计划于2月8日10:00开始的分发时段订阅人数已超过3000人已经确认有人在等待。</p><p>此外，还发布了针对被ANYCOLOR解约的Zaion LanZa的<strong>指控</strong>文件（俗称“<strong>锡安文件</strong>”）的<strong>Sayu</strong>频道的订阅人数截至2月7日7:00。自2月4日以来，病例数增加了5,000多例，达到约43,700例。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="lNAUJs0yDi"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-sayu-officially-debut-zaion-document-publisher/">VTuber Sayu正式出道，作为“Zion文件”的发布者而受到关注</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Sayu正式出道，作为“Zion文件”的发布者而受到关注” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-sayu-officially-debut-zaion-document-publisher/embed/#?secret=AVPbfULed0#?secret=lNAUJs0yDi" data-secret="lNAUJs0yDi" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p>在海外，Seren Ryugetsu的合同终止引发了ANYCOLOR的激烈批评。因此，最近Dokibird和Sayu频道订阅人数的快速增长可以被认为是支持这些人才的愿望的表达。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"> https://twitter.com/dokibird/status/1754763901064093867?s=20 </div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="QrvUG8MBV3"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/wikipedia-x-account-post-a-criticizing-nijisanji-anycolor-as-a-black-company/">维基百科的X账户发表帖子批评Nijisanji和ANYCOLOR是黑人公司？</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Wikipedia X 帐户发表了一篇文章，批评 Nijisanji/ANYCOLOR 是一家黑人公司” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/wikipedia-x-account-post-a-criticizing-nijisanji-anycolor-as-a-black-company/embed/#?secret=7wkrIQtMhZ#?secret=QrvUG8MBV3" data-secret="QrvUG8MBV3" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="6pyQPSJq4S"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/studio-nekomata-ended-handling-of-nijisanji-related-goods-due-to-protest-against-selen-tatsuki-terminated/">Studio Nekomata已停止处理与Nijisanji相关的商品以抗议Seren Ryugetsu的合同被取消？</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Studio Nekomata 已停止处理与 Nijisanji 相关的商品。这是 Seren Ryugetsu 合同被取消后的抗议吗？” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/studio-nekomata-ended-handling-of-nijisanji-related-goods-due-to-protest-against-selen-tatsuki-terminated/embed/#?secret=3hv9ZQeP7o#?secret=6pyQPSJq4S" data-secret="6pyQPSJq4S" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://youtube.com/@Dokibird" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">多奇鸟</a>/<a href="https://x.com/dokibird" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">多奇<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f3c6.png" alt="🏆" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></a></p> <cite>YouTube/X（推特）</cite></blockquote><p> （ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“Mr.2”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="6w6GSpIlTI"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/dokibird-supposed-actor-of-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-has-a-spike-in-youtube-subscribers/">Dokibird（VTuber Selen Tatsuki 的假定演员）的 YouTube 订阅人数激增</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Dokibird（VTuber Selen Tatsuki 的假定演员）的 YouTube 订阅人数激增” — P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/dokibird-supposed-actor-of-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-has-a-spike-in-youtube-subscribers/embed/#?secret=PbwgoI1G6z#?secret=6w6GSpIlTI" data-secret="6w6GSpIlTI" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p>后<a href="https://p2y.jp/dokibird-supposed-actor-of-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-has-a-spike-in-youtube-subscribers/">VTuber Seren Ryugetsu的表演者/声音模型“Dokibird”频道订阅者迅速增加</a>首先出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/dokibird-supposed-actor-of-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-has-a-spike-in-youtube-subscribers/feed/ 0 114169
